    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnatjone Domini millesimo octoagesimo octavo,
                        anno quinto Deo propitjo pontificatus domni <persName key="#Popes"
                            ref="#people/4301">Clementis</persName> pape in apostolica sacratisima
                        sede beati Petri apostoli, inperante vero <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/77">Henrico</persName> filio quondam Einritj i(n)peratoris
                        anno quinto, die vigesimosexto mensis aprelis, inditjone undetjma,
                            <placeName ref="#places/594" key="#Cities">Ravenne</placeName>. Quia
                        petistis a vobis in Dei nomine <persName key="#Monks"><name
                                ref="Gherardus Pomposianus">Gerardo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monacho</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Rent_in_money
                            #Penalty #Books #Fruits/vegetables #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in
                                <placeName ref="#places/4179">Pomposea</placeName></orgName>, uti
                        mihi presenti in Christi nomine <persName><name ref="Petrus de Carbone"
                                >Petro de Carbone</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Berta"
                                >Berte</name></persName> iugalibus seu liberis nostris legitimis vel
                        naturalibus âˆ’ et qualis ex nobis obierit sine liberis eius portjo cadat
                        alteri qui supravixerit usque ad annos quinquaginta ad renovandum per hanc
                        paginam pacti concedistis nobis rem iuris vestri monasterii, idest <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">unum spatjum terre integrum</rs> positum in ac
                            <rs key="#Cities">tjvitate</rs> Ravenne, in regione Porte Nove, extens
                            <rs key="#Size">in longitudinem suam pedibus legitimis quadraginta, in
                            latitudinem viginti et novem</rs>; a duobus lateribus posidente
                            <persName key="#Confinia"><name ref="Albertus de Romaldi">Alberto filio
                                quondam Romaldi</name></persName> iure vestri monasterii, a tertjo
                            <rs key="#Confinia #Roads">via publica</rs> atque a quarto latere <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Fruits/vegetables">orto vestro domnicato</rs>. Habendum,
                        tenendum, posidendum, defensandum et in omnibus meliorandum, sub pensione
                        quam vobis et vestris successoribus dare debeamus pro predicto spatjo omni
                        martjo mense aut infra inditjone <rs key="#Rent_in_money">den(arios)
                            Ven(eticos) sex tantum</rs>. Pro eo quia exinde accepistis, caltjarii
                        nomine, <rs key="#Books">librum</rs> unum pro <rs key="#Price">den(ariorum) 
                            Ven(eticorum) solidis decem</rs>;
                        sub pene nomine <rs key="#Penalty">[au]ri untjam unam</rs> ex.</ab>
                </div>
